name: Shoresy
overview: Foul-mouthed, chirp-serving, mother-loving, fan favourite character, Shoresy, joins the Sudbury Bulldogs of the Northern Ontario Senior Hockey Organization (The NOSHO) on a quest to never lose again.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: In Season 3, Shoresy and the Sudbury Blueberry Bulldogs compete in the National Senior Tournament, facing off against teams from across Canada, like the Charlottetown Reds, Brooks Barrelmen, Vaughan Canadesi, and SOO Hunt.

episodes.name: Never Lose Again
episodes.overview: Shoresy tries to prevent his team from folding.

episodes.name: Veteran Presence
episodes.overview: Shoresy and his new recruits attend a mixer at Nat’s, the General Manager of the Sudbury Bulldogs.

episodes.name: Know Your Role
episodes.overview: The Bulldogs face off against the Timmins Timber Kings and the infamous Apeldoorn brothers.

episodes.name: If You Can’t Win, Don’t Play
episodes.overview: Shoresy attends his family reunion and the Bulldogs play the North Bay Norsemen.

episodes.name: Hockey Brings People Together
episodes.overview: The Bulldogs face the powerhouse Soo Cyclones.

episodes.name: Don’t Poke the Bear
episodes.overview: The Soo Cyclones return for the Bulldogs final game of the season.

episodes.name: Get 'Em Focused
episodes.overview: The Bulldogs focus on a league record.

episodes.name: Skill vs. Will
episodes.overview: The Bulldogs prepare to play the new American team.

episodes.name: Set the Tone
episodes.overview: The Bulldogs face off against the Soo Hunt and their veteran presence.

episodes.name: Players Only
episodes.overview: Shoresy starts putting out fires with a players only meeting.

episodes.name: The Man Advantage
episodes.overview: Shoresy faces judgment from the league.

episodes.name: Accountability
episodes.overview: The Bulldogs cross the border for the final game of the season against the Soo Hunt.
The National Senior Tournament begins and the Bulldogs are hurt.

episodes.overview: The Bulldogs play the Charlottetown Reds and their captain Gorgeous Gord Gallant.

episodes.name: Brooks Barrelmen
episodes.overview: The Bulldogs celebrate their NOSHO record and take on the Brooks Barrelmen and the Freezer twins.

episodes.name: SOO Hunt
episodes.overview: The Bulldogs attempt to redeem themselves against the SOO Hunt.
